<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَعُل يفْعُل، بالضم<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[همزة]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[وَطُؤ]</span> فراشُه وطاءةً فهو وطيء،<span class="c5"> بالهمز:</span> أي لين غير خشن.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
